"in the tests, mostly QEMU binaries or to control the behavior of the tests. "
"Environment variables are set automatically by the build system, but it can "
"be useful to alter them when running tests manually. The following are the "
"environment variables recognized by QTest, not including test-specific ones:"
msgstr ""

